[00:00.03] A regular citizen who reports
[00:02.64] Seeing a crime isn't a snitch or a rat
[00:06.30] The criminals were just sloppy
[00:09.08] Snitches and rats are not the same thing
[00:12.14] Let me break it down to make sure y'all see what I mean
[00:15.79] A snitch is someone minding other folks' business
[00:19.83] To find information they can sell for a price
[00:23.78] Or trade for some other form of compensation
[00:27.11] A rat is a traitor, a conceiver, planner or physical participator
[00:35.96] He doesn't sell secrets for power or cash
[00:39.15] He betrays the trust of his team or his family
[00:44.56] Hoping to save his own cowardly ass
[00:47.62] The difference is, at least a snitch is human
[00:53.35] But a rat is a... rat, period
[00:57.03] 